Fireshirt, a list open web app.

P1:
    Cross-platform support
    Touch gestures
    CSS3 animations

    Creating new lists
    Adding/deleting/editing/arranging items in a list
    Navigating between lists (swipes, dropdown)
    Fading peripheral elements when adding/editing an item

    AppCache and localStorage
    Save state of last accessed list

P2:
    Loading page
    Expo view of lists, activated via pinch

    Sub-items

P3:
    Landing page (show all lists in a list)
